headline: Allstate CEO to Present at Goldman Sachs 2025 U.S. Financial Services Conference
summary: NORTHBROOK, Ill., November 21, 2025--The Allstate Corporation (NYSE: ALL) announced that Tom Wilson, its Chair, President and Chief Executive Officer, will present at the Goldman Sachs U.S. Financial Services Conference at 7 a.m. CT on Wednesday, Dec. 10.
